=== 开发 ===
[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]前夕，鉴于两部前作的巨大票房成功<ref name="gross">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=312&catName=TGlmZXRpbWU= |title=Top Lifetime Grossers Worldwide (IND Rs) |publisher=Box Office India |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021202725/http://www.boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=312&catName=TGlmZXRpbWU= |archivedate=2013-10-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Box Office 2004|url=http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=210&catName=MjAwNA==|publisher=Box Office India|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014132208/http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=210&catName=MjAwNA==|archivedate=2013-10-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Dhoom (2004) |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dhoom/ |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2012-01-06 |archive-date=2011-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222014021/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dhoom/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite web|title=Dhoom 3 'dhoom' drowns Aamir-starrer 'Talaash'|url=http://www.emirates247.com/bollywood/take-one/dhoom-3-dhoom-drowns-aamir-starrer-talaash-2011-12-29-1.434974|publisher=Emirates 24/7|quote=If you ask anyone about my next release . everyone seems to be talking about ''Dhoom 3'' only and honestly, we haven't even shot a single frame of the film|date=2011-12-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414100928/http://www.emirates247.com/bollywood/take-one/dhoom-3-dhoom-drowns-aamir-starrer-talaash-2011-12-29-1.434974|archivedate=2012-04-14}}</ref>，影片享受到媒体的广泛报道<ref>{{cite web|title=Deepika Padukone in talks for 'Dhoom 3'|url=http://www.supergoodmovies.com/26479/bollywood/deepika-padukone-in-talks-for-dhoom-3-news-details|publisher=SuperGood Movies|accessdate=2012-01-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923071254/http://www.supergoodmovies.com/26479/bollywood/deepika-padukone-in-talks-for-dhoom-3-news-details|archivedate=2013-09-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The Biggest 'Big Story'|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-12-30/news-interviews/30569244_1_controversies-preeti-jain-dhoom|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2012-01-04|date=2011-12-30|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103185913/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-12-30/news-interviews/30569244_1_controversies-preeti-jain-dhoom|dead-url=no}}</ref>，从而在观众和媒体中引发期待<ref name="#1"/>。2011年1月2日，《幻影车神》电影系列前作制片人阿迪亚·乔普拉证实第三部《幻影车神》将于2011年末开机。最初，制片方和男主角阿米尔想在2012年圣诞节发布电影<ref name="Dhoom4">{{cite news|title=Aamir is the villain in Dhoom:3|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-02-02/news-interviews/28365712_1_dhoom-3-aamir-khan-jai-dixit|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2011-02-03|date=2011-02-02|archive-date=2013-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402160010/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-02-02/news-interviews/28365712_1_dhoom-3-aamir-khan-jai-dixit|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但主要由于预测显示在圣诞节发行会让后期制作进度非常赶，不利于给予电影高标准的技术需求，于是改在2013年初发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/2011/10/17/16493/index.html|title=Dhoom 3 release shifted to 2013 on 25th december|work=Bollywood Hungama|date=2011-10-07|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2011-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019030401/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/2011/10/17/16493/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片单是制片就要花费约12.5亿卢布（2000万美元）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficeindia.com/Details/art_detail/isaamirkhantherealsuperstarnowasheistheonlyonetotakeabigopeningwithoutbackingofaholidaywithdhoom3|title=Is Aamir Khan The Real Superstar Now As He Is The Only One To Take A Big Opening Without Backing of a Holiday With Dhoom 3?|publisher=[[Box_Office_India|Box Office India]]|date=2014-01-30|accessdate=2014-01-30|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201215417/http://www.boxofficeindia.com/Details/art_detail/isaamirkhantherealsuperstarnowasheistheonlyonetotakeabigopeningwithoutbackingofaholidaywithdhoom3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据报道，乔普拉想以[[3D|3D]]制作电影，他观察到此前以该格式发布的宝莱坞电影所取得的成功。然而，演员阿米尔·汗认为，3D技术需要专业知识，担心导演利用这一技术的后果<ref>{{cite news|title=Dhoom 3 in 3D? Aamir hesitant...|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-05-26/news-interviews/29582229_1_3d-aamir-khan-first-film|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2011-10-29|date=2011-05-26|archive-date=2013-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110131518/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-05-26/news-interviews/29582229_1_3d-aamir-khan-first-film|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2012年9月，YRF Studios尚未宣布以3D制作电影<ref>{{cite news|title=3D movies: Bollywood gives a new dimension|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-11-07/computing/30369386_1_3d-glasses-theatre-owners|accessdate=2011-11-28|newspaper=The Times of India|date=2011-11-17|author=Ameya Chumbhale|author2=Nandini Raghavendra|archive-date=2014-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114065824/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-11-07/computing/30369386_1_3d-glasses-theatre-owners|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 选角 ===
阿米尔·汗签约合同出演[[反派|反派]]主角，而阿彼锡·巴克罕和尤代·乔普拉证实出演警察角色<ref name=Nomom>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan to play villain in Dhoom 3|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/aamir-khan-to-play-villain-in-dhoom-3/809915|work=The Indian Express|accessdate=2013-02-25|archive-date=2013-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908063105/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/aamir-khan-to-play-villain-in-dhoom-3/809915|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡特丽娜·卡芙签约合同出演正派女主角。他学会了芭蕾舞<ref>{{cite news|title=Aamir getting trained for his ballet dancing act for 'Dhoom 3'|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/tamil/article/73720.html|accessdate=2011-11-08|newspaper=IndiaGlitz|date=2011-11-08|archive-date=2017-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028094018/https://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/tamil/article/73720.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[特技飞行|特技飞行表演]]<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-14/news-interviews/32234777_1_aamir-khan-dhoom-yrf | title=Aamir takes the plunge | date=2012-06-14 | work=The Times of India | accessdate=2015-07-20 | archive-date=2013-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029213129/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-14/news-interviews/32234777_1_aamir-khan-dhoom-yrf | dead-url=no }}</ref>和法国[[跑酷|跑酷]]技术<ref>{{cite news|last=LALWANI|first=VICKEY|title=Aamir learns French technique of Parkour|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-11-18/news-interviews/30414207_1_aamir-khan-parkour-dhoom-franchise|accessdate=2011-11-24|newspaper=Mumbai Mirror|date=2011-11-18|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103083700/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-11-18/news-interviews/30414207_1_aamir-khan-parkour-dhoom-franchise|dead-url=no}}</ref>——这种运动方法主要是用速度和效率解决障碍，卡芙则要上滑翔伞训练课和声乐课<ref>{{cite web |author=Your name: |url=http://www.emirates247.com/bollywood/buzz/bollywood-buzz-aamir-katrina-s-dhoom-3-prep-2011-10-17-1.423842 |title=Bollywood Buzz: Aamir & Katrina's 'Dhoom 3' prep |publisher=Emirates 24/7 |date=2011-10-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120617095133/http://www.emirates247.com/bollywood/buzz/bollywood-buzz-aamir-katrina-s-dhoom-3-prep-2011-10-17-1.423842 |archivedate=2012-06-17 }}</ref>。巴克罕据称为了准备他在片中的角色，减肥减了9公斤<ref>{{cite web |url=http://goindocal.com/abhishek-bachchan-loses-9-kgs-for-dhoom-3go-2973.htm |title=GoIndoCal News Entertainment " Bollywood -Abhishek Bachchan loses 9 kgs for Dhoom 3 |publisher=Goindocal.com |accessdate=2011-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425232740/http://goindocal.com/abhishek-bachchan-loses-9-kgs-for-dhoom-3go-2973.htm |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref>。扮演ACP杰·迪克西尔妻子的[[利米·森|利米·森]]表示即便向她提供角色，她也不会出演<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/rimi-sen-left-out-of-dhoom-3/article1-1048985.aspx | title=Rimi Sen left out of Dhoom 3? | work=Hindustan Times | date=2013-04-23 | accessdate=2014-01-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113115009/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/rimi-sen-left-out-of-dhoom-3/article1-1048985.aspx | archivedate=2014-01-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-18/news-interviews/32298656_1_comic-roles-comedies-cameo| title=No more guest appearances| work=The Times of India| format=Interview| date=2012-06-18| accessdate=2012-06-19| author=Vohra, Meera| archive-date=2013-10-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029213647/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-18/news-interviews/32298656_1_comic-roles-comedies-cameo| dead-url=no}}</ref>。与前两部的导演[[山杰·葛达威|山杰·葛达威]]不一样的是，系列电影的编剧维贾伊·克里希纳·阿查里亚将导演第三部作品<ref name=Nomom />。特技导演奥利维尔·凯勒（{{lang|en|Olliver Keller}}）签约指导动作场面<ref>{{cite news|title=Bollywood blockbusters hire Hollywood talent|url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?section=Movies&Id=306172&keyword=bollywood&subcatg=MOVIESINDIA&nid=306172|accessdate=2012-12-24|newspaper=NDTV Movies|date=2011-11-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130129190804/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?section=Movies&Id=306172&keyword=bollywood&subcatg=MOVIESINDIA&nid=306172|archivedate=2013-01-29}}</ref>。阿米尔·汗接受采访时表示，他在片中的角色是迄今为止他的演艺生涯中最难演的角色。动作场面由康拉德·帕尔米萨诺和山姆·卡尤沙尔导演<ref>{{cite web|title=Credits – DHOOM:3|url=http://www.dhoom3.net/credits.html|work=YRF|access-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705051142/http://www.dhoom3.net/credits.html|archive-date=2015-07-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在接受[[印度亚洲通讯社|印度亚洲通讯社]]采访时，阿彼锡·巴克罕解释了片中的每一个角色是如何的明显：“《幻影车神》是我的电影，我是里面的英雄。没人能把我从电影中赶出去。你可以是最出名或是最不起眼的明星，但《幻影车神》是杰和阿里的故事，它就是那样的简单。如果《幻影车神》没有杰和阿里的角色，那电影就不存在了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/dhoom-3-is-my-film-and-i-am-the-hero-abhishek-bachchan/439715-8-66.html |title='Dhoom 3' is my film and I am the hero: Abhishek Bachchan |publisher=Ibnlive.in.com |date=2013-12-15 |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2014-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301135321/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/dhoom-3-is-my-film-and-i-am-the-hero-abhishek-bachchan/439715-8-66.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”2013年9月23日，距离影片正式上映还有三个月，DNA和其他新闻媒体透露阿米尔·汗将在片中饰演双重角色，但他们当时并没有证实这一消息，直至影片发行时，阿米尔·汗确实在片中饰演双重角色。这使得本片成为系列中目前唯一一部有双重反派角色的作品<ref>{{cite web |author=Upala KBR |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-aamir-khans-twin-avatar-in-dhoom-3-1892645 |title=Aamir Khan's twin avatar in 'Dhoom 3'! |work=Daily News and Analysis |date=2013-09-23 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219022742/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-aamir-khans-twin-avatar-in-dhoom-3-1892645 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/508213/20130923/aamir-khan-double-role-dhoom-3.htm |title=Aamir Khan in Double Role for 'Dhoom 3'? |publisher=Ibtimes.co.in |date=2013-09-23 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218231632/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/508213/20130923/aamir-khan-double-role-dhoom-3.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-09-24/news-interviews/42359279_1_double-role-aamir-khan-dhoom-3 |title=Aamir Khan has a double role in 'Dhoom 3'? |work=The Times of India |date=2013-09-24 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927135454/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-09-24/news-interviews/42359279_1_double-role-aamir-khan-dhoom-3 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/double-whammy-for-aamir-khans-fan-to-play-double-role-in-dhoom-3/1/311476.html |title=Double whammy for Aamir Khan's fans, he will play double role in Dhoom 3 |work=India Today |date=2013-09-24 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227030300/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/double-whammy-for-aamir-khans-fan-to-play-double-role-in-dhoom-3/1/311476.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.koimoi.com/bollywood-popular/aamir-khan-to-play-a-double-role-in-dhoom-3/ |title=Aamir Khan To Play A Double Role in Dhoom 3? |publisher=Koimoi.com |date=2013-09-24 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218114847/http://www.koimoi.com/bollywood-popular/aamir-khan-to-play-a-double-role-in-dhoom-3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://zoomtv.indiatimes.com/news/dhoom-3-aamir-may-be-seen-in-a-double-role/articleshow/23000680.cms |title=Dhoom 3: Aamir may be seen in a double role |work=The Times of India |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219184841/http://zoomtv.indiatimes.com/news/dhoom-3-aamir-may-be-seen-in-a-double-role/articleshow/23000680.cms |archive-date=2014-02-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ghose |first=Daliya |url=http://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/aamir-in-double-role-in-dhoom-3/12733/ |title=Aamir Khan in double role in 'Dhoom 3' |publisher=Bollywoodmantra.com |date=2013-09-25 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219065650/http://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/aamir-in-double-role-in-dhoom-3/12733/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，本片并不是系列电影首次出现双重角色，[[比帕莎·巴苏|比帕莎·巴苏]]在《[[幻影车神2|幻影车神2]]》中出演了蔏娜丽和蒙娜丽双重角色，但并不像汗那样在同一场景中出现。

=== 拍摄 ===
