拍摄定于2011年11月开始，涉及阿彼锡·巴克罕和尤代·乔普拉的场景将率先开机<ref>{{cite news|title=No Dhoom without Uday and me: Abhishek|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/No-Dhoom-without-Uday-and-me-Abhishek/Article1-769305.aspx|accessdate=2011-11-18|newspaper=Hindustan Times|date=2011-11-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117175506/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/No-Dhoom-without-Uday-and-me-Abhishek/Article1-769305.aspx|archivedate=2011-11-17}}</ref>，但阿彼锡正在放产假，因此拍摄被推迟到2012年1月。2012年1月，由于主角阿米尔此前承诺过电视节目《[[真相访谈|真相访谈]]》（{{lang|en|''Satyamev Jayate''}}），日程被推到2012年6月；到了6月份，拍摄日程又推迟了一个月，给汗准备他的体操运动员角色。此外，汗想要集中于他的2012年电影《[[觅迹寻踪|觅迹寻踪]]》（{{lang|en|''Talaash: The Answer Lies Within''}}）<ref>{{cite news|title=Aamir Khan can't do Dhoom before July|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-12-31/news-interviews/30575969_1_aamir-khan-talaash-reema-kagti|newspaper=Mumbai Mirror|date=2011-12-31|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2012-07-07|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707152109/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-12-31/news-interviews/30575969_1_aamir-khan-talaash-reema-kagti|dead-url=no}}</ref>。没有任何进一步的推延因素后，2012年6月8日孟买雅什·拉吉影片公司与杰奇·史洛夫和阿米尔·汗童年角色扮演者席德哈特夫·尼嘉姆。阿米尔·汗于2012年7月假如剧组，在雅什·拉吉电影公司进行为期五日的拍摄后，转到芝加哥及其他美国城市。随后，汗、阿彼锡·巴克罕、尤代·乔普拉于2012年8月4日飞往美国，完成三个月的拍摄。2012年12月回到印度时，巴克罕表示拍摄进度已经过半，影片将在孟买再度开机<ref>{{cite news|title=Dhoom 3 is 50 per cent complete: Abhishek Bachchan|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Dhoom-3-is-50-per-cent-complete-Abhishek-Bachchan/Article1-974457.aspx|newspaper=Hindustan Times|date=2012-12-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121220032124/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Dhoom-3-is-50-per-cent-complete-Abhishek-Bachchan/Article1-974457.aspx|archivedate=2012-12-20}}</ref>。2013年3月第二周，据报道剧组成员将离开印度前往瑞士[[苏黎世|苏黎世]]和[[提契诺州|提契诺州]]拍摄高潮场景<ref>{{cite news|title=Aamir Khan to join Katrina Kaif in Switzerland shoot|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Aamir-Khan-to-join-Katrina-Kaif-in-Switzerland-shoot/Article1-1023155.aspx|newspaper=Hindustan Times|date=2013-03-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310100458/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Aamir-Khan-to-join-Katrina-Kaif-in-Switzerland-shoot/Article1-1023155.aspx|archivedate=2013-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Aamir Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Uday Chopra in Switzerland|url=http://www.indicine.com/movies/bollywood/aamir-khan-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra-in-switzerland/|work=Indicine|date=2013-03-16|accessdate=2013-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054224/http://www.indicine.com/movies/bollywood/aamir-khan-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra-in-switzerland/|archive-date=2013-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。影片于2013年9月14日在孟买郊区的电影工作室杀青<ref>{{cite web|last=Mangaokar|first=Shalvi|title=Aamir Khan wraps up Dhoom:3 shooting, gets emotional|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/aamir-khan-wraps-up-dhoom-3-shooting-gets-emotional/article1-1122721.aspx|work=Hindustan Times|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223093923/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/aamir-khan-wraps-up-dhoom-3-shooting-gets-emotional/article1-1122721.aspx|archivedate=2013-12-23}}</ref>。影片的高潮场景在瑞士提契诺州著名的拱坝[[康特拉水坝|康特拉水坝]]（俗称韦尔扎斯卡大坝）拍摄<ref name="ContraDhoom3">{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/12/31/dhoom-3-review-bollywood-s-baffling-blockbuster.html|title='Dhoom 3' Review: Bollywood’s Baffling Blockbuster|publisher=thedailybeast.com|date=2013-12-31|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629115523/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/12/31/dhoom-3-review-bollywood-s-baffling-blockbuster.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]的特技演员在1995年电影《[[黄金眼|黄金眼]]》的开头场景中从大坝一跃而下，使大坝成为热门蹦极场所<ref>[http://www.filmapia.com/published/scenes/jumping-dam "Jumping off the dam (Dhoom3)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmapia.com/published/scenes/jumping-dam |date=20140322001355 }}, ''Filmapia''</ref>。

== 发行 ==
2013年11月，阿迪亚·乔普拉传出信息称电影将在全国开启“Go digital or miss Dhoom 3”巡展。在详细声明中他表示：“电影将透过数字渠道及UFO数字电影院发行，为防盗版还用上水印标记和可追溯的指纹。据称电影的盗版拷贝正被运往国内外的影院。数字电影院为限制盗版，将被泄露的“偷跑”内容删掉。这也使得制片方在拍摄场景时从经济上而言节省了大量的打印成本。除此之外，加密内容保护了分销商和制片商的版权。数码冲印能防止印刷品重复，帮助电影院回流资金<ref>{{cite news|title=No Dhoom 3 at theatres that don't have digital facility: Aditya Chopra|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-no-dhoom-3-at-theatres-that-don-t-have-digital-facility-aditya-chopra-1915342|date=2011-11-07|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-no-dhoom-3-at-theatres-that-don-t-have-digital-facility-aditya-chopra-1915342|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Film pirates, beware! 'Dhoom 3' is out of your reach now|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/film-pirates-beware-dhoom-3-is-out-of-your-reach-now_146042.html|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630123016/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/film-pirates-beware-dhoom-3-is-out-of-your-reach-now_146042.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='Dhoom:3’ launch gets IMAX push|url=http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/55pjksDaG5PdQgUMjXtdOO/Dhoom3-launch-gets-IMAX-push.html|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712191705/http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/55pjksDaG5PdQgUMjXtdOO/Dhoom3-launch-gets-IMAX-push.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |agency=Indo-Asian News Service |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Dont-show-Dhoom-3-illegally-Delhi-court/articleshow/26786592.cms |title=Don't show 'Dhoom 3' illegally: Delhi court |work=The Times of India |date=2013-12-03 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204010514/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Dont-show-Dhoom-3-illegally-Delhi-court/articleshow/26786592.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[IMAX|IMAX]]公司和雅什·拉吉影片公司宣布《幻影车神3》将是首部以IMAX格式发行的第一部印度本土语言作品。这部电影采用IMAX专有的数字重新掌握技术数字修复IMAX格式，在全印度和全球各地的部分IMAX影院发行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/131224/entertainment-bollywood/article/prasads-not-always-imax |title=Prasads is not always an IMAX |work=Deccan Chronicle |date=2013-12-23 |accessdate=2013-12-23 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224105123/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/131224/entertainment-bollywood/article/prasads-not-always-imax |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://epaper.deccanchronicle.com/articledetailpage.aspx?id=235937 |title=Prasads is not always an IMAX |work=Deccan Chronicle |date=2013-12-23 |accessdate=2013-12-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224105808/http://epaper.deccanchronicle.com/articledetailpage.aspx?id=235937 |archivedate=2013-12-24 }}</ref>。电影将以电影院音响技术[[杜比全景声|杜比全景声]]发行。雅什·拉吉影片公司给予影片优异的全景声混音技术。2013年12月12日，影片被[[英国电影分级委员会|英国电影分级委员会]]授予表示中度暴力的12A认证<ref name="BBFC">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/dhoom-3-2013 |title=DHOOM 3 | British Board of Film Classification |publisher=Bbfc.co.uk |date=2013-12-10 |accessdate=2013-12-18 |archive-date=2013-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219030624/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/dhoom-3-2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片在全印度的4500块屏幕（包括[[泰米尔语|泰米尔语]]和[[泰卢固语|泰卢固语]]版）及海外的750块屏幕上映<ref name="Live Mint">{{cite web | url=http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/7K3WaBJHUg2nawEWnNvVOI/All-eyes-and-wallets-on-Dhoom-3-this-Friday.html | title=All eyes (and wallets) on Dhoom: 3 this Friday | work=Nandini Ramnath | publisher=Live Mint | date=2013-12-17 | accessdate=2013-12-18 | archive-date=2013-12-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218074424/http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/7K3WaBJHUg2nawEWnNvVOI/All-eyes-and-wallets-on-Dhoom-3-this-Friday.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片还在[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]的250块屏幕上映<ref name="Budget, low PR, hike in ticket prices">{{cite web | url=http://www.business-standa