ttp://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mangalore/Made-in-Udupi-Dhoom-3-game-logs-5m-downloads/articleshow/28026930.cms|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2013-11-15|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mangalore/Made-in-Udupi-Dhoom-3-game-logs-5m-downloads/articleshow/28026930.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏自发布以来，三个月内获得1000万次下载<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-dhoom-3-the-game-crosses-10-million-mobile-downloads-1961536 |title='Dhoom: 3 The Game' crosses 10 million mobile downloads |work=Daily News and Analysis |date=2014-02-12 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302020812/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-dhoom-3-the-game-crosses-10-million-mobile-downloads-1961536 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmsofindia.com/viewnews-3345 |title='Dhoom:3 The Game' Crosses 10 Million Downloads |publisher=Filmsofindia.com |accessdate=2014-04-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307115304/http://www.filmsofindia.com/viewnews-3345 |archivedate=2014-03-07 }}</ref>。

