uring-aamir-khan-katrina-kaif-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra/1/324796.html |archivedate=2013-12-07 }}</ref>。2013年11月14日，首支宣传歌曲《放手去爱》（{{lang|en|Malang}}）发布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.koimoi.com/bollywood-popular/dhoom-3-song-malangs-first-look-revealed-feat-aamir-khan-katrina-kaif/ |title=Dhoom 3 Song Malang's First Look Revealed |publisher=KoiMoi.com |date=2013-11-25 |accessdate=2015-08-08 |archive-date=2015-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629134523/http://www.koimoi.com/bollywood-popular/dhoom-3-song-malangs-first-look-revealed-feat-aamir-khan-katrina-kaif/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿米尔·汗与其他舞蹈演员跳踢踏舞打节拍的片花《Dhoom Tap》于2013年12月3日。由卡特里娜·卡芙主演、苏尼迪·乔汉（{{lang|en|Sunidhi Chauhan}}）演唱的歌曲《为爱沉迷》（{{lang|en|Kamli}}）的片花发布。由[[香卡·马哈德温|香卡·马哈德温]]（{{lang|en|Shankar Mahadevan}}）12岁的儿子锡万·马哈德温（{{lang|en|Shivam Mahadevan}}）及阿尼什·夏尔马（{{lang|en|Anish Sharma}}）演唱的歌曲《上帝恩赐》（{{lang|en|Bande Hain Hum Uske}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2014-01-17/news-and-interviews/46299889_1_dhoom-3-title-song-siddharth|title=I never want to be treated as a star kid: Shivam Mahadevan|work=The Times of India|date=2014-01-09|accessdate=2014-01-15|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140202131454/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2014-01-17/news-and-interviews/46299889_1_dhoom-3-title-song-siddharth|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。其长子席德哈特夫·马哈德温（{{lang|en|Siddharth Mahadevan}}）和阿尼什·夏尔马演唱了《放手去爱》一曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/musicindia/dhoom-3-watch-aamir-katrinas-stunning-aerial-act-in-malang-promo_147012.html |title='Dhoom 3': Watch Aamir, Katrina's stunning aerial act in 'Malang' promo |publisher=Zeenews.india.com |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217224050/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/musicindia/dhoom-3-watch-aamir-katrinas-stunning-aerial-act-in-malang-promo_147012.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主题曲《举世震撼》的阿拉伯语版由黎巴嫩歌手娜雅（{{lang|en|Naya}}）演唱<ref>{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Dhoom-macha-le-goes-Arabic/articleshow/27124863.cms |title=Dhoom macha le goes Arabic! |work=The Times of India |date=2013-12-09 |accessdate=2013-12-15 |archive-date=2016-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Dhoom-macha-le-goes-Arabic/articleshow/27124863.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

