电影在国内获得的评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web|title=Dhoom 3 Is Now The Fastest 100 Cr Club Entrant {{!}} Beats Chennai Express' Record|url=http://www.koimoi.com/box-office/dhoom-3-is-now-the-fastest-100-cr-entrant-beats-chennai-express-record/|publisher=[[Koimoi|Koimoi]]|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://www.koimoi.com/box-office/dhoom-3-is-now-the-fastest-100-cr-entrant-beats-chennai-express-record/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Dhoom 3' rakes in around 40 crores on opening day!|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/dhoom-3-rakes-in-around-40-crores-on-opening-day_148080.html|publisher=[[Zee_News|Zee News]]|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/dhoom-3-rakes-in-around-40-crores-on-opening-day_148080.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[宝莱坞星闻|宝莱坞星闻]]（{{lang|en|''Bollywood Hungama''}}）的塔兰·阿达尔什（{{lang|en|Taran Adarsh}}）打出4.5星（满分5星，下同）的评价，表示：“总的来说，影片有着具备态度和明星力量的可靠演员阵容，让系列的粉丝垂涎三尺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/reviews/type/view/id/1330 |title=Dhoom 3 | Latest Hindi Movie Review by Taran Adarsh |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220230258/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/reviews/type/view/id/1330 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《巴斯卡日报》（{{lang|en|Daily Bhaskar}}）打出4.5星。在赞扬汗表演的同时，该报写道：“整个电影建立在汗的肩膀上，不会有说汗强大得能独自坚持三个小时的高度评价<ref>{{cite web |url=http://daily.bhaskar.com/article-hf/ENT-movie-review-dhoom-3-aamir-khan-didnt-steal-in-the-film-he-stole-the-whole-film--4470289-NOR.html |title=Movie review Dhoom 3: Only 2 heroes – Aamir Khan & the bikes in a lacklustre, loop-holed film but surprisingly you'll enjoy it |publisher=daily.bhaskar.com |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223111927/http://daily.bhaskar.com/article-hf/ENT-movie-review-dhoom-3-aamir-khan-didnt-steal-in-the-film-he-stole-the-whole-film--4470289-NOR.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Koimoi|Koimoi]]的莫哈尔·巴苏（{{lang|en|Mohar Basu}}）打出4星，表示影片“壮观雄伟”<ref>{{cite web|last=Basu|first=Mohar|title=Dhoom 3 Review|url=http://www.koimoi.com/reviews/dhoom-3-review/|work=[[Koimoi|Koimoi]]|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918224623/http://www.koimoi.com/reviews/dhoom-3-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[印度时报|印度时报]]》的苏丽佳娜·米特拉·达斯（{{lang|en|Srijana Mitra Das}}）打出4星，特别赞赏演员的表演：“影片让你欢笑，让你喘息——甚至是抽鼻子”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/movie-review/27677238.cms |title=Dhoom 3 movie review: Wallpaper, Story, Trailer at Times of India |work=The Times of India |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221223905/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/movie-review/27677238.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Zee_News|Zee News]]的阿帕娜·穆迪（{{lang|en|Aparna Mudi}}）打出4星，表示“影片设法以现代手法演绎宝莱坞经典复仇故事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/dhoom-3-review-an-aamir-khan-film-all-the-way_148041.html |title='Dhoom 3' Review: High octane action, Bollywood style |publisher=Zeenews.india.com |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223054455/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/dhoom-3-review-an-aamir-khan-film-all-the-way_148041.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[每日新闻评论|每日新闻评论]]》（{{lang|en|''Daily News and Analysis''}}）的萨利塔·腾沃尔（{{lang|en|Sarita A Tanwar}}）也给出4星评价，并评论道：“欢迎来到这个令人瞠目结舌和从未在印度电影中出现的动作特技世界。影片以尽可能伟大的方式重新定义了“娱乐”一词<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/review-film-review-dhoom-3-redefines-the-word-entertainment-in-the-grandest-way-possible-1938325 |title=Film review: 'Dhoom 3' redefines the word 'entertainment' in the grandest way possible – Entertainment – DNA |work=Daily News and Analysis |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222023000/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/review-film-review-dhoom-3-redefines-the-word-entertainment-in-the-grandest-way-possible-1938325 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”另一方面，[[NDTV|NDTV]]的塞拜·查特杰（{{lang|en|Saibal Chatterjee}}）给出3星，指影片“是一部高压动作片，完全依赖流派的惯用手法”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie-reviews/dhoom-3-movie-review-907 |title=Dhoom: 3 movie review | NDTV Movies.com |publisher=Movies.ndtv.com |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221205208/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie-reviews/dhoom-3-movie-review-907 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]]的苏坎亚·瓦尔玛（{{lang|en|Sukanya Verma}}）给出3星，称影片“延续了冒险片铺张浪费的传统，费用都花在挑剔的最新反派明星阿米尔·汗的绳降上<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/sukanya-verma-reviews-dhoom-3-mazaa-le/20131220.htm |title=Sukanya Verma reviews Dhoom 3: Mazaa Le! |publisher=Rediff.com |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222044722/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/sukanya-verma-reviews-dhoom-3-mazaa-le/20131220.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[印度电影观众|印度电影观众]]的拉奇特·古普塔（{{lang|en|Rachit Gupta}}）打出3星，尽管他将其标榜为“外表光滑的电影”，但他认为“驱动他们的动力、剧情、舞蹈都很糟糕”<ref>{{cite web |date=20 December 2013 |url=http://www.filmfare.com/reviews/movie-review-dhoom3-4986.html |title=Movie review: Dhoom:3 |publisher=Filmfare.com |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220221924/http://www.filmfare.com/reviews/movie-review-dhoom3-4986.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]]》的[[阿努帕玛·丘普拉|阿努帕玛·丘普拉]]（{{lang|en|Anupama Chopra}}）给出3星评价，写道：“第三部......比前两部更盛大更注重剧情<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/movie-review-by-anupama-chopra-dhoom-3-is-worth-watching/article1-1164955.aspx#sthash.R8PVSzML.dpuf |title=Movie review by Anupama Chopra: Dhoom 3 high on glamour, low on logic |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2013-12-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226233235/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/movie-review-by-anupama-chopra-dhoom-3-is-worth-watching/article1-1164955.aspx#sthash.R8PVSzML.dpuf |archivedate=2013-12-26 }}</ref>。”[[印度亚洲通讯社|印度亚洲通讯社]]的评论由《[[商务标准报|商务标准报]]》（{{lang|en|Business Standard}}）转发，给出了3星，称影片“是一部有趣的作品......纤细、柔软、聪明、微妙......然而被吸引尖叫声的中心表演掌舵<ref>{{cite web |author=IANS  20 December 2013 Last Updated at 23:30 IST |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/dhoom-3-intriguing-enrapturing-unfinished-ians-hindi-film-review-113122001033_1.html |title='Dhoom 3': Intriguing, Enrapturing , Unfinished... (IANS Hindi Film Review) |work=Business Standard |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223072504/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/dhoom-3-intriguing-enrapturing-unfinished-ians-hindi-film-review-113122001033_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

负面评价兼而有之<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/dPBQFifgOBbNurJpv7LiwN/For-filmmakers-PRs-the-rising-star.html |title=For film-makers, PR's the rising star |publisher=Livemint |date=2013-12-26 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718121917/http://www.livemint.com/Consumer/dPBQFifgOBbNurJpv7LiwN/For-filmmakers-PRs-the-rising-star.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Saptarishi Dutta|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/indiarealtime/2013/12/20/review-roundup-critics-doom-dhoom-3/|work=The Wall Street Journal|title=Review Roundup: Critics Doom ‘Dhoom: 3′|date=2013-12-20|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://blogs.wsj.com/indiarealtime/2013/12/20/review-roundup-critics-doom-dhoom-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[CNN-IBN|CNN-IBN]]的拉杰夫·马萨德（{{lang|en|Rajeev Masand}}）打出2.5星，表示影片“被一个简单的剧本降低等级，它无法提供实在的娱乐。”他称影片“草率的照搬稿子三明治，夹杂着过火的表演和潇洒的对话”，缺乏前部的“刺激感”<ref>{{cite web|last=Masand|first=Rajeev|title='Dhoom 3' review: The film is a sloppily scripted sandwich of hammy acting|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/dhoom-3-review-the-film-is-a-sloppily-scripted-sandwich-of-hammy-acting/440755-47-77.html|publisher=CNN-IBN|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2014-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301201744/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/dhoom-3-review-the-film-is-a-sloppily-scripted-sandwich-of-hammy-acting/440755-47-77.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Rediff|Rediff]]的拉贾·森（{{lang|en|Raja Sen}}）打出1.5星。批评反派的动机和“让人打哈欠的追车场面”，都有“毫无意义的糟糕剪辑”，他认为影片是“为没看过电影的小屁孩制作的儿童电影”<ref>{{cite web|last=Masand|first=Rajeev|title=Raja Sen reviews Dhoom 3: It's dumber than the first two!|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/raja-sen-reviews-dhoom-3-its-dumber-than-the-first-two/20131220.htm|publisher=[[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]]|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924151433/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/raja-sen-reviews-dhoom-3-its-dumber-than-the-first-two/20131220.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[印度快报|印度快报]]》的舒布拉·笈多（{{lang|en|Shubhra Gupta}}）打出2星。尽管他赞赏“摄影一流、画面养眼、海外取景地广阔”，但他认为影片“是系列作品疲劳感和极为缺乏想象力的受害者”。笈多还认为汗缺乏“反派性感的恶性”，注意到卡芙的角色不太重要<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/movie-review-dhoom-3-is-more-bust-than-boom/1209912/0 |title='Dhoom 3' review: Aamir Khan doesn't have the sexy-badness |work=The Indian Express |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223051104/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/movie-review-dhoom-3-is-more-bust-than-boom/1209912/0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[印度今日|印度今日]]》的罗希特·可汗林纳尼（{{lang|en|Rohit Khilnani}}）严厉批评影片，打出2星，表称其“漏洞遍布，夸张的表演和过分的动作场面放在所有的时间点都不合适”。他认为影片唯一的补充因素是异国情调和特效带来的“视觉享受”<ref name="indiatoday">{{cite web|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/dhoom-3-movie-review-aamir-khan-katrina-kaif-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra/1/332052.html|title=Movie review: Dhoom 3 is a visual treat but that's about it|work=India Today|date=2013-12-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022040814/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/dhoom-3-movie-review-aamir-khan-katrina-kaif-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra/1/332052.html|archivedate=2014-10-22}}</ref>。《论坛快报》（{{lang|en|''Express Tribune''}}）的拉法叶·马哈茂德（{{lang|en|Rafay Mahmood}}）打出1.5星，指出“俏皮话过量”，缺乏“连接妥当的因果关系链”，“建立了过量的没有显著意义的动作场面”。他特别批评演员的表演。马哈茂德称卡芙的小对话“华而不实”，认为汗“或许给出了他职业生涯中最糟糕的表演”<ref>{{cite web |last=Mahmood |first=Rafay |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/649941/dhoom-3-aamir-khan-succumbs-to-low-brow-cinema/ |title=Dhoom 3: Aamir Khan succumbs to low-brow cinema |work=The Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517025144/http://tribune.com.pk/story/649941/dhoom-3-aamir-khan-succumbs-to-low-brow-cinema/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

与此同时，影片还获得外国影评人的赞赏。评论聚合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据9条评论，给影片打出78%的新鲜度，评级得分8.2/10<ref>{{cite web|title=Dhoom 3 (2013)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dhoom_3/|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101101301/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dhoom_3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志的大卫·丘特（{{lang|en|David Chute}}）赞扬摄像、动作、特技和阿米尔的表演：“阿查亚的镜头似乎能和演员一道跳舞和狂笑......高飞杂技和阿米尔·汗出色的表演主导了宝莱坞最知名动作系列的第三部<ref>{{cite news |author=David Chute |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-dhoom-3-1200983530/ |title=Film Review: ‘Dhoom: 3′ |work=Variety |accessdate=2013-12-23 |archive-date=2013-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223071834/http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-dhoom-3-1200983530/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的比尔·斯塔门特表示，“影片是大快人心的民粹主义表演”，“追逐场景、抢劫银行、魔术场景和歌舞表演都很娱乐”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/24488634-421/dhoom3-packs-action-less-cgi-in-film.html |title='Dhoom:3’ packs action, less CGI, in film |work=Chicago Sun-Times |accessdate=2013-12-23 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224202859/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/24488634-421/dhoom3-packs-action-less-cgi-in-film.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。许多影评人指出影片与[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]作品《[[致命魔术|致命魔术]]》和《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》的近似点<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-dhoom-3-1200983530/|title=Film Review: 'Dhoom: 3'|work=Variety|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130134926/http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-dhoom-3-1200983530/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/dhoom-3-review-roundup-aamir-khan-gives-christopher-nolans-prestige-bollywood-treatment-1429944 |title=Dhoom 3 Review Roundup: Aamir Khan Gives Christopher Nolan's Prestige a Bollywood Treatment |work=International Business Times |date=2013-12-21 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101064032/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/dhoom-3-review-roundup-aamir-khan-gives-christopher-nolans-prestige-bollywood-treatment-1429944 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/dhoom-3-review-starring-aamir-khan-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra-katrina-kaif/1/332102.html |title=Movie review: Dhoom 3 on par with Hollywood's action flicks : Reviews, News |work=India Today |date=2013-12-20 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223043718/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/dhoom-3-review-starring-aamir-khan-abhishek-bachchan-uday-chopra-katrina-kaif/1/332102.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/raja-sen-reviews-dhoom-3-its-dumber-than-the-first-two/20131220.htm |title=Raja Sen reviews Dhoom 3: It's dumber than the first two! |publisher=Rediff.com |date=2013-12-20 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430041908/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/raja-sen-reviews-dhoom-3-its-dumber-than-the-first-two/20131220.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Abrams |first=Simon |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/dhoom-3-2013 |title=Dhoom: 3 Movie Review & Film Summary (2013) |publisher=Roger Ebert |date=2013-12-23 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328162450/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/dhoom-3-2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

